This is a simple GenericMode for XModMap files:

    (define-generic-mode 'xmodmap-mode
      '(?!)
      '("add" "clear" "keycode" "keysym" "pointer" "remove")
      nil
      '("[xX]modmap\\(rc\\)?\\'")
      nil
      "Simple mode for xmodmap files.")


Suggestion to include it in Emacs: http://emacsbugs.donarmstrong.com/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=2065

